3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-rain-live-updates-schools-shut-delhi-on-red-alert-as-rain-fury-continues-6236191%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-rain-live-updates-schools-shut-delhi-on-red-alert-as-rain-fury-continues-6236191%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-rain-live-updates-schools-shut-delhi-on-red-alert-as-rain-fury-continues-6236191%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%20Meeting%3A%20What%20Prompted%20Conflict%20in%20Mega%20Auction%20Discussion%20With%20BCCI%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20IPL%20team%20owners%20were%20divided%20in%20their%20opinions%20on%20issues%20ranging%20from%20the%20mega%20auction%20to%20the%20impact%20substitute%20player%20rule%20when%20they%20met%20with%20the%20BCCI%20officials%20here%20on%20Wednesday.%20With%20the%20mega%20auction%20slated%20to%20be%20held%20ahead%20of%20the%2018th%20edition%20of%20the%20T20%20league%20next%20year%2C%20the%20BCCI%20had%20called%20for%20a%20meeting%20here%20at%20its%20headquarters%20to%20discuss%20the%20pointers%20and%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20confirmed%20the%20same%20after%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20on%20Wednesday%20organised%20a%20constructive%20dialogue%20with%20the%20owners%20of%20the%2010%20franchises%20on%20various%20subjects%20pertaining%20to%20the%20upcoming%20season%20of%20the%20IPL%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20franchise%20owners%20tabled%20feedback%20on%20player%20regulations%20and%20other%20commercial%20aspects%2C%20including%20central%20merchandising%2C%20licensing%2C%20and%20gaming.%20The%20BCCI%20will%20now%20take%20these%20recommendations%20to%20the%20IPL%20Governing%20Council%20for%20further%20deliberation%20and%20evaluation%20before%20formulating%20the%20IPL%20player%20regulations%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20added%20in%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeams%20are%20not%20likely%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20retain%20more%20than%20five%20players%20with%20one%20Right%20to%20Match%20(RTM)%20card.%20The%20RTM%20card%20gives%20a%20franchise%20the%20opportunity%20to%20match%20the%20final%20bid%20of%20a%20player%20from%20their%20squad%20of%20the%20previous%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20secretary%20later%20confirmed%20to%20the%20media%20that%20the%20board%20will%20be%20taking%20its%20decisions%20soon%20on%20all%20the%20points%20that%20were%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20team%20owners%20or%20co-owners%20who%20attended%20the%20meeting%20were%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20from%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%2C%20Kavya%20Maran%20from%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%2C%20Ness%20Wadia%20from%20Punjab%20Kings%2C%20Sanjiv%20Goenka%20with%20his%20son%20Shashwat%20from%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%2C%20KK%20Grand%20and%20Parth%20Jindal%20from%20Delhi%20Capitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoj%20Badale%20and%20Ranjit%20Barthakur%20from%20Rajasthan%20Royals%2C%20Prathamesh%20Mishra%20from%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%2C%20Kari%20Viswanathan%20and%20Rupa%20Gurunath%20from%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%2C%20Amit%20Soni%20from%20Gujarat%20Titans%20while%20Mumbai%20Indians'%20owners%20attended%20it%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWadia%20and%20SRK%20had%20a%20heated%20debate%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20whether%20to%20have%20a%20mega%20auction%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Parth%20Jindal%2C%20the%20director%20of%20JSW%20Sports%20which%20owns%20the%20Delhi%20Capitals%2C%20said%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20real%20outcome%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20meeting%20as%20the%20teams%20looked%20to%20stick%20to%20their%20opinions%20on%20all%20the%20matters%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20real%20outcome.%20It%20was%20just%20to%20hear%20all%20the%20different%20perspectives%20from%20all%20the%20owners%20and%20the%20BCCI%20has%20heard%20us%20and%20now%20they%20will%20give%20us%20all%20the%20rules.%20Hopefully%2C%20by%20the%20end%20of%20August%20we%20will%20get%20to%20know%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20next%20cycle%2C%26quot%3B%20Jindal%20told%20the%20reporters%20here%20at%20the%20BCCI%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJindal%20confirmed%20there%20was%20no%20consensus%20among%20the%20teams%20in%20context%20of%20the%20number%20of%20players%20they%20wanted%20to%20retain%20ahead%20of%20the%20mega%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20(on%20the%20consensus).%20Some%20people%20want%20eight%20to%2010%2C%20some%20people%20want%20four%2C%20some%20people%20want%20six%E2%80%A6%20it's%20all%20up%20in%20the%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJindal%20confirmed%20there%20was%20a%20debate%20whether%20there%20should%20be%20an%20auction%20in%20the%20IPL%20at%20all%2C%20while%20adding%20that%20Delhi%20Capitals%20are%20not%20against%20having%20an%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%2C%20yeah%2C%20I%20was%20surprised.%20There%20was%20a%20debate.%20Some%20people%20said%20that%20there%20should%20not%20be%20a%20mega%20auction%20at%20all.%20There%20should%20be%20only%20smaller%20auctions%2C%26quot%3B%20Jindal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20in%20that%20camp.%20I%20feel%20that%20it%20(auction)%20evens%20the%20playing%20field%20and%20it's%20very%20good%20for%20everyone.%20It%20makes%20the%20IPL%20what%20it%20is.%20It%20makes%20it%20competitive.%20It%20makes%20it%20an%20even-playing%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20on%20the%20same%20page%20on%20many%20issues.%20But%20I%20think%20the%20BCCI%2C%20in%20their%20wisdom%2C%20will%20decide.%20I%20think%20the%20president%20and%20secretary%20will%20decide%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJindal%20also%20expressed%20the%20opinion%20that%20Delhi%20Capitals%20are%20against%20the%20impact%20player%20rule%20while%20providing%20his%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImpact%20player%20rule%2C%20again%2C%20(there%20were)%20different%20views%20from%20different%20people.%20Some%20people%20want%20it%20because%20it%20gives%20a%20chance%20to%20young%20players%20to%20play%20in%20the%20IPL.%20Some%20people%20don't%20want%20it%20because%20it%20is%20detrimental%20to%20Indian%20cricket%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20development%20of%20all-rounders%20so%20it's%20a%20mixed%20bag%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20in%20the%20second%20camp.%20I%20don't%20want%20it.%20I%20prefer%20the%20game%20as%20it%20is%20%E2%80%94%2011%20versus%2011.%20I%20think%20all-rounders%20are%20very%20important.%20You%20have%20different%20players%20who%20don't%20bowl%20in%20the%20IPL%20or%20don't%20bat%20in%20the%20IPL%20because%20of%20this%20rule%2C%20which%20is%20not%20good%20for%20Indian%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20Jindal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20Kings'%20Wadia%20hoped%20the%20decisions%20will%20be%20taken%20in%20favour%20of%20%26quot%3Ball%20stakeholders%26quot%3B%20while%20adding%20that%20the%20matter%20of%20overseas%20players'%20availability%20was%20also%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20discussed%20several%20points%2C%20auctions%2C%20players%2C%20uncapped%20players.%20It%20was%20a%20good%20meeting%2C%20happy%20to%20be%20having%20a%20discussion%20with%20the%20BCCI%20and%20whatever%20will%20be%20done%20will%20be%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20fans%2C%20players%20and%20all%20the%20stakeholders%2C%26quot%3B%20Wadia%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722485820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fkqrek4m8_ness-wadia-preity-zinta-bcci_625x300_01_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fipl-2025-auction-meeting-who-said-what-on-retention-impact-player-rule-and-mo