he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fhome-news%2Fkate-middleton-cancer-lump-removal-princess-wales-b2588167.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndependent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20shared%20by%20royal%20author%20Rob%20Jobson%20in%20his%20upcoming%20book%2C%20'Catherine%2C%20the%20Princess%20of%20Wales'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApart%20from%20debilitating%20bouts%20of%20morning%20sickness%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20stays%20in%20the%20Lindo%20Wing%20at%20St%20Mary's%20Hospital%20to%20deliver%20her%20babies%2C%20Catherine%20has%20fortunately%20avoided%20hospital%20for%20most%20of%20her%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jobson%20explained.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20teenager%2C%20however%2C%20when%20at%20Marlborough%20College%20she%20discovered%20a%20lump%20on%20the%20left%20side%20of%20her%20head%2C%20just%20under%20her%20hairline%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20added%20that%20her%20mother%20took%20her%20to%20the%20hospital%20where%20the%20doctors%20removed%20it.%20%26quot%3BThe%20school%20notified%20her%20parents%20immediately%20and%20her%20mother%20Carole%20took%20her%20to%20hospital%2C%20where%20she%20had%20surgery%20to%20remove%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20operation%20left%20a%20three-inch%20scar%20which%20several%20people%20noticed%20on%20Ms%20Middleton's%20first%20solo%20engagement%20over%20two%20decades%20ago.%20The%20Buckingham%20Palace%20shared%20a%20brief%20statement%20that%20read%2C%20%26quot%3B'The%20scar%20is%20related%20to%20a%20childhood%20operation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Princess%20said%20in%20June%20that%20she%20was%20making%20good%20progress%20as%20she%20was%20undergoing%20preventative%20chemotherapy.%20However%2C%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20out%20of%20the%20woods%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20personal%20written%20message%2C%20Ms%20Middleton%20said%20she%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bblown%20away%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20thousands%20of%20kind%20messages%20from%20across%20the%20globe%20which%20followed%20her%20cancer%20announcement%20in%20March.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20making%20good%20progress%2C%20but%20as%20anyone%20going%20through%20chemotherapy%20will%20know%2C%20there%20are%20good%20days%20and%20bad%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20those%20bad%20days%20you%20feel%20weak%2C%20tired%20and%20you%20have%20to%20give%20in%20to%20your%20body%20resting.%20But%20on%20the%20good%20days%2C%20when%20you%20feel%20stronger%2C%20you%20want%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20feeling%20well.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20they%20had%20made%20a%20world%20of%20difference%20to%20her%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20heir-to-the-throne%20Prince%20William.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20treatment%20is%20ongoing%20and%20will%20be%20for%20a%20few%20more%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20looking%20forward%20to%20attending%20The%20King's%20Birthday%20Parade%20this%20weekend%20with%20my%20family%20and%20hope%20to%20join%20a%20few%20public%20engagements%20over%20the%20summer%2C%20but%20equally%20knowing%20I%20am%20not%20out%20of%20the%20woods%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20on%20June%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Princess%20of%20Wales%20was%20recently%20seen%20at%20the%20Wimbledon%20Men's%20final%20in%20London%20as%20she%20walked%20onto%20the%20court%20to%20present%20the%20trophy%20to%20winner%20Carlos%20Alcaraz.%20A%20passionate%20tennis%20fan%20and%20player%20herself%2C%20Kate%20was%20greeted%20with%20a%20thunderous%20ovation%20as%20she%20entered%20the%20Royal%20Box%20at%20Centre%20Court%2C%20accompanied%20by%20her%20daughter%20Princess%20Charlotte%20and%20sister%20Pippa%20Matthews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722477240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ff5dovut8_kate-middleton-reuters_625x300_23_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22http