s%20to%20match%20the%20lofty%20achievements%20of%20the%20champion%20cricketer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20top-three%20finish%20in%20the%2050m%20rifle%20three%20positions%20final%20here%20on%20Thursday%20would%20certainly%20put%20Kusale%20in%20the%20list%20of%20high%20achieves%20in%20Indian%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20follow%20anyone%20specific%20in%20the%20shooting%20world.%20Outside%20of%20that%2C%20I%20admire%20Dhoni%20for%20the%20person%20that%20he%20is.%20My%20sport%20requires%20me%20to%20be%20as%20calm%20and%20patient%20as%20he%20is%20on%20the%20field.%20I%20also%20relate%20to%20his%20story%20as%20I%20am%20a%20ticket%20collector%20like%20he%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20Kusale%20told%20PTI%20shortly%20after%20finishing%20seventh%20in%20a%20tightly%20contest%20qualification%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKusale%20has%20been%20working%20for%20Central%20Railways%20since%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20two%20rivals%20from%20Czech%20Republic%20also%20shot%20590%20but%20the%20Indian%20had%20the%20most%20inner%2010s%20--%2038%20--%20compared%20to%20Jiri%20Privratsky%20and%20Petr%20Nymbursky%2C%20who%20sealed%20the%20eighth%20and%20last%20qualification%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20doesn't%20have%20to%20look%20too%20far%20beyond%20home%20for%20inspiration.%20His%20father%20and%20brother%20are%20teachers%20in%20a%20district%20school%20while%20mother%20is%20the%20sarpanch%20of%20Kambalwadi%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fancied%20Aishwary%20Pratap%20Tomar%20ended%2011th%20with%20a%20total%20of%20589%20in%20a%20session%20topped%20by%20China's%20Liu%20Yukun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKusale%20did%20not%20know%20about%20his%20classification%20in%20the%20final%20until%20his%20coach%20told%20him%20that.%20He%20shot%20197%20in%20prone%2C%20195%20in%20standing%20and%20as%20much%20in%20kneeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20shot%20is%20a%20new%20shot.%20I%20was%20just%20trying%20to%20be%20patient.%20The%20whole%20match%20I%20had%20the%20same%20mindse