nd%20Russia%20bubbled%20up%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20prison%20officials%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussian-uk-dissident-kara-murza-disappears-jail-latest-sign-prisoner-swap-with-2024-07-31%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Vladimir%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-critic-vladimir-kara-murza-arrested-in-moscow-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKara-Murza%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Russian%20dissident%20and%20Putin%20rival%20who%20was%20imprisoned%20for%20criticizing%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20was%20moved%20from%20the%20penal%20colony%20in%20Siberia%20where%20he%20was%20being%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20among%20several%20prisoners%20who%20have%20recently%20been%20moved%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-russian-arctic-prison-where-alexey-navalny-spent-last-days-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussian%20prisons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fueling%20the%20mounting%20speculation%20that%20a%20prisoner%20swap%20was%20coming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20and%20US%20officials%20have%20not%20confirmed%20that%20a%20prisoner%20swap%20is%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20reached%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20referred%20to%20comments%20made%20at%20its%20press%20briefing%20on%20Wednesday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20reports%20of%20political%20prisoners%20in%20Russia%20being%20moved%20around%2C%20Vedant%20Patel%2C%20a%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20speculate%20on%20any%20reasoning.%20What%20I%20can%20say%20is%20that%20the%20United%20States%20continues%20to%20be%20focused%20on%20working%20around%20the%20clock%20to%20work%20to%20get%20our%20wrongfully%20detained%20American%20citizens%20home%2C%20and%20that%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20case%2C%20but%20have%20no%20updates%20beyond