d-trump-falsely-suggest-kamala-harris-misled-voters-about-her-race%2Famp_articleshow%2F112181032.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BKerala%20Paying%20Price%20Of...%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP%20Leader%20On%20Wayanad%20Landslides%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%C2%A0BJP%20leader%20V%20Muraleedharan%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan-led%20Kerala%20government%20over%20the%20recent%20landslides%20in%20Wayanad%20that%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20over%20160%20people%20and%20said%20that%20state%20was%20paying%20the%20price%20of%20the%20state%20government's%20'casual%20approach.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20assertion%20in%20Parliament%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20state%20was%20warned%20as%20early%20as%20July%2023%20about%20a%20potential%20natural%20calamity%20in%20Wayanad%20due%20to%20heavy%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%20on%20the%20Wayanad%20landslide%20incidents%2C%20BJP%20leader%20V%20Muraleedharan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHome%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20very%20specifically%20mentioned%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%20stands%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Kerala%20like%20a%20rock%20and%20there%20can%20be%20no%20doubt%20about%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmit%20Shah%20also%20said%20that%20had%20the%20Kerala%20government%20worked%20with%20alertness%20when%20the%20NDRF%20battalions%20landed%2C%20that%20would%20have%20saved%20a%20lot.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20blame%20anyone%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20put%20the%20facts%20before%20the%20house%2C%20saying%20that%20on%20July%2023%2C%2024%2C%2025%20and%2026%20of%20July%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20issued%20warnings%20and%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20be%20prepared%20and%20initiate%20the%20evacuation%20of%20people%2C%20but%20the%20Kerala%20government%20didn't%20heed%20the%20warning%20messages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20further%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMoreover%2C%20many%20agencies%20in%20the%20past%20have%20been%20alerted%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20landslides%20in%20the%20area.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20Kerala%20disaster%20management%20authority%20warned%20that%20there%20was%20an%20impending%20tragedy%20and%20advised%20relocating%204%2C000%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Muraleedharan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20village%20of%20Mundakkai%2C%20which%20has%20now%20been%20affected%20by%20the%20landslide%2C%20was%20identified%20as%20one%20of%20the%2018%20landslide-prone%20places%20in%20the%20district%20disaster%20management%20plan.%20But%20the%20state%20government%20did%20not%20pay%20heed%20to%20it%20and%20now%20Kerala%20is%20paying%20the%20price%20because%20of%20the%20casual%20approach%20of%20the%20state%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Muraleedharan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20area%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20an%20ecologically%20sensitive%20area.%20Despite%20that%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%20300%20illegal%20construction%20projects%20in%20the%20area.%20No%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20remove%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20disaster%20sparked%20a%20heated%20exchange%20of%20words%20among%20political%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20CM%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20refuted%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20assertion%20in%20Parliament%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20state%20was%20warned%20as%20early%20as%20July%2023%20about%20a%20potential%20natural%20calamity%20in%20Wayanad%20due%20to%20heavy%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20the%20time%20to%20blame%20each%20other.%20However%2C%20reports%20from%20the%C2%A0Rajya%20Sabha%20indicate%20that%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20claimed%20they%20had%20issued%20a%20warning%2C%20and%20Kerala%20did%20not%20respond%20appropriately%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Kerala%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20in%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vijayan%20stated%20that%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20had%20only%20issued%20an%20orange%20alert%20for%20the%20district%20prior%20to%20the%20landslides.%20However%2C%20Wayanad%20experienced%20over%20500%20millimetres%20of%20rainfall%2C%20far%20exceeding%20the%20IMD's%20predictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20massive%20landslides%20struck%20Wayanad%2C%20Kerala%2C%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20causing%20extensive%20destruction%2C%20rescue%20operations%20are%20being%20intensified%2C%20political%20leaders%20are%20engaged%20in%20discussions%2C%20and%20financial%20aid%20is%20being%20mobilised%20for%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20landslide%20occurred%20in%20Mundakkai%2C%20a%20town%2C%20and%20the%20second%20in%20Chooralmala.%20The%20massive%20landslides%20wreaked%20havoc%20in%20the%20region%2C%20damaging%20houses%20and%20roads%2C%20uprooting%20trees%2C%20and%20swelling%20water%20bodies%2C%20which%20hindered%20rescue%20operations.%20Relief%20and%20rescue%20efforts%20are%20currently%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landslides%20in%20Mundakkai%20and%20Chooralmala%2C%20Wayanad%2C%20have%20resulted%20in%20167%20confirmed%20deaths%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Kerala%20Revenue%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Information%20and%20Public%20Relations%20(PRD)%20Control%20Room%20in%20Wayanad%2C%2096%20victims%20have%20been%20identified%2C%20including%2077%20men%2C%2067%20women%2C%20and%2022%20children.%20Post-mortem%20examinations%20have%20been%20conducted%20on%20166%20bodies%20and%2049%20body%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2075%20bodies%20have%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20relatives.%20Rescue%20personnel%20have%20brought%20219%20individuals%20to%20hospitals%3B%2078%20are%20still%20receiving%20treatment%2C%20while%20142%20have%20been%20moved%20to%20relief%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Wayanad%2C%2073%20people%