C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20of%20downplaying%20her%20Indian%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20know%20she%20was%20Black%20until%20a%20number%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20she%20happened%20to%20turn%20Black%2C%20and%20now%20she%20wants%20to%20be%20known%20as%20Black%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20president%20said%20of%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20she%20Indian%20or%20is%20she%20Black%3F%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fi%2Fbookmarks%3Fpost_id%3D1818714936979108309%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20former%20president%20asked%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(The%20vice%20president%20is%20of%20Indian%20and%20Jamaican%20heritage.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Trump%20was%20asked%20by%20ABC%20News%20journalist%20Rachel%20Scott%20if%20Harris%20was%20a%20%26quot%3BDEI%26quot%3B%20hire%20%E2%80%94%20a%20term%20that%20some%20Republicans%20have%20lobbed%20against%20Harris%20to%20invalidate%20her%20qualifications%20for%20president%20due%20to%20her%20gender%20and%20race%20%E2%80%94%20he%20said%20that%20he%20was%20unsure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20don't%20know%2C%20could%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20then%20defended%20his%20vice-presidential%20selection%20of%20Ohio%20Sen.%20JD%20Vance%2C%20attacked%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20cognitive%20abilities%2C%20and%20accused%20Harris%20of%20not%20passing%20her%20bar%20exam.%20(Harris%20passed%20the%20exam%20on%20her%20second%20try%2C%20which%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20her%20career%20as%20a%20San%20Francisco%20district%20attorney%20and%20California%20attorney%20general.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20conversation%2C%20many%20members%20argued%20that%20having%20an%20open%20forum%20with%20the%20GOP%20presidential%20contender%20was%20exactly%20what%20journalists%20should%20facilitate%2C%20regardless%20of%20his%20myriad%20controversies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Trump's%20remarks%20will%20likely%20only%20further%20polarize%20many%20within%20the%20organization%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20former%20president%20took%20digs%20at%20the%20equipment%20used%20for%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mics%20are%20really%20in%20lousy%20shape%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20one%20point.%20%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20understand%20what%20you're%20saying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20conversation%20has%20heightened%20pressure%20on%20the%20NABJ%20from%20its%20members%20over%20the%20Trump%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENABJ%20President%20Ken%20Lemon%20in%20a%20statement%20Tuesday%20said%20that%20the%20organization%20had%20been%20in%20talks%20with%20Harris'%20team%20for%20an%20in-person%20panel%20before%20she%20became%20the%20presumptive%20Democratic%20presidential%20nominee.%20But%20he%20said%20that%20the%20organization%20was%20told%20that%20such%20a%20request%20could%20not%20be%20fulfilled%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20virtual%20option%20was%20also%20something%20that%20the%20Harris%20team%20couldn't%20accommodate%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELemon%20then%20said%20that%20NABJ%20would%20work%20to%20schedule%20a%20panel%20with%20Harris%20before%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20April%20Ryan%2C%20the%20White%20House%20correspondent%20for%20The%20Grio%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAprilDRyan%2Fstatus%2F1818617610797212155%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20NABJ%20leadership%20informed%20Harris'%20team%20that%20it%20was%20preferable%20that%20she%20be%20in-person%20for%20her%20appearance.%20Ryan%20also%20reported%20that%20NABJ%20later%20approached%20Harris%20about%20holding%20a%20virtual%20town%20hall%2C%20but%20that%20the%20vice%20president's%20team%20had%20%26quot%3Bmoved%20on%26quot%3B%20after%20their%20earlier%20request%20for%20a%20virtual%20option%20was%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type