20his%20dogged%20defense%20with%20a%20very%20high%20back%20lift.%20Between%201974%20and%201984%2C%20he%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20game%20of%20musical%20chair%20with%20Chetan%20Chauhan%20for%20the%20role%20of%20second%20opener%20to%20partner%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20in%20the%20Indian%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20genial%20personality%2C%20he%20scored%20a%20double%20hundred%20against%20Imran%20Khan's%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20was%20one%20of%20the%20slowest%20double%20tons%20of%20that%20time.%20The%20match%20was%20played%20at%20Jalandhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bespectacled%20opener%2C%20Gaekwad's%20finest%20hour%20came%20while%20facing%20a%20young%20Michael%20Holding%20and%20Wayne%20Daniel%20at%20Sabina%20Park%20in%20Jamaica%20in%20the%201976%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHolding's%20beamer%20hit%20him%20on%20the%20ear%20and%20as%20he%20lay%20smeared%20in%20blood%2C%20home%20team%20supporters%20were%20shouting%20from%20the%20tree%20top%20%26quot%3BKill%20him%20Maaan..Kill%20him%20Mikey%26quot%3B%2C%20something%20Gavaskar%20termed%20as%20Barbarism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20he%20was%20coach%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%20between%201998%20and%201999%20and%20Kumble's%2010-for%20at%20Kotla%20happened%20with%20him%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoung%20Harbhajan%20Singh%20made%20his%20Test%20debut%20under%20him%20and%20always%20spoke%20with%20reverence%20about%20'Angshu%20sir'%20for%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20he%20carried%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20served%20as%20national%20selector%2C%20headed%20the%20Baroda%20Cricket%20Association%20and%20just%20before%20he%20fell%20ill%2C%20he%20was%20the%20BCCI%20Apex%20Council%20member%20as%20an%20ICA%20representative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECricket%20legends%20such%20as%20Gavaskar%2C%20Kapil%20Dev%2C%20former%20India%20coach%20Ravi%20Shastri%2C%20Clive%20Lloyd%2C%20Andy%20Roberts%2C%20Farokh%20Engineer%2C%20ex-India%20skipper%20Dilip%20Vengsarkar%2C%20BCCI%20president%20Roger%20Binny%2C%20Mohinder