0should%20be%20a%20mega%20auction%20before%20IPL%202025%20at%20all%2C%20Wadia%20was%20completely%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20complete%20overhaul.%20The%20report%20further%20claimed%20that%20Wadia%20felt%20that%20there%20should%20be%20very%20less%20retentions%20for%20each%20side%20-%20a%20point%20that%20was%20not%20to%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20liking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20owners%20who%20attended%20the%20meetings%20were%20-%C2%A0Kiran%20Kumar%20Grandhi%20of%20Delhi%20Capitals%2C%20Sanjiv%20Goenka%20of%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%2C%20Rupa%20Gurunath%20of%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%2C%20Kavya%20Maran%20of%20SunRisers%20Hyderabad%20and%20Manoj%20Badale%20of%20Rajasthan%20Royals.%20Few%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20team%20winners%20including%20the%20Ambanis%20of%20Mumbai%20Indians%20attended%20the%20BCCI%20meeting%20through%20video%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0during%20the%20previous%C2%A0IPL%C2%A0season%20this%20year%2C%20there%20were%20eight%20250-plus%20totals%2C%20including%20the%20total%20of%20287%20runs%20posted%20by%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20(SRH)%20against%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%2C%20the%20highest-ever%20in%20league's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20critics%2C%20players%20and%20experts%20expressed%20their%20dissatisfaction%20with%20the%20Impact%20Player%20rule%2C%20blaming%20it%20for%20such%20unprecedented%20six-hitting%20and%20for%20stunting%20the%20growth%20of%20all-rounders%20as%20team's%20often%20chose%20to%20use%20a%20pure%20batter%2Fbowler%20through%20this%20role%20instead%20of%20an%20all-rounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20rule%20was%20introduced%20back%20in%202023%20season%20and%20allows%20players%20to%20pick%20an%20extra%20specialist%20batter%2Fbowler%20depending%20on%20the%20situation.%20Nine%20of%20the%20ten%20highest%20total%20in%20league's%20history%20have%20come%20after%20this%20rule's%20introduction%2C%20highlighting%20the%20freedom%2C%20power%20and%20flexibility%20it%20ad