%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Frafael-nadal-carlos-alcaraz-vs-rajeev-ram-austin-krajicek-live-score-mens-doubles-tennis-quarter-finals-match-today-paris-olympics-2024-live-updates-6232126%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEither%20You%20Will%20Survive%20Or%20I%20Will%26quot%3B%3A%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20To%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVirtually%20kickstarting%20the%20campaign%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20President%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20on%20Wednesday%20challenged%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BEither%20you%20will%20survive%20or%20I%E2%80%9D%2C%20triggering%20a%20protest%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20pre-election%20preparatory%20meeting%20of%20party%20workers%20and%20leaders%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20endured%20everything%20but%20stood%20firm%20and%20taught%20the%20BJP%20a%20lesson%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20party%20was%20broken%2C%20we%20were%20targeted%20by%20central%20probe%20agencies%2C%20money%20power%20was%20used%20against%20us%2C%20and%20they%20even%20wanted%20to%20throw%20us%20in%20jail%E2%80%A6%20But%20we%20survived%20everything%20and%20emerged%20victorious%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20amid%20thunderous%20applause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20chief%20minister%20recalled%20how%20ex-Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20Home%20Minister%20Anil%20Deshmukh%20had%20informed%20him%20that%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20was%20'conspiring'%20to%20dump%20both%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Aditya%20Thackeray%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%20warned%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20act%20straight%20we%20shall%20be%20straight%2C%20but%20if%20you%20play%20crooked%2C%20we%20shall%20do%20likewise.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20either%20you%20will%20stay%20or%20I%20will%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20reminded%20the%20gathering%20how%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20unitedly%20won%204%20out%20of%206%20LS%20seats%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20opposition's%20performance%20made%20the%20top%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20uncomfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CListening%20to%20PM%20Modi's%20speeches%20has%20become%20painful%20now%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20BJP's%20charges%20of%20getting%20only%20minority%20votes%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20narrated%20an%20incident%20where%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Muslims%20were%20present%20and%20he%20asked%20them%20if%20they%20had%20reservations%20about%20him%20being%20a%20Hindu%20or%20his%20idea%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20and%20they%20unanimously%20said%20%E2%80%98no'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20BJP%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bparty%20of%20crooks%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20claimed%20that%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20he%20met%20many%20national%20Opposition%20leaders%20like%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20who%20paid%20compliments%20to%20him%20by%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CUddhavji%2C%20you%20have%20shown%20a%20direction%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20never%20elected%20as%20a%20municipal%20corporator%2C%20I%20directly%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%A6%20I%20did%20everything%20possible.%20This%20(Assembly%20elections)%20is%20the%20last%20challenge%20for%20you.%20They%20broke%20the%20party.%20Sena%20is%20not%20a%20rusty%20sword%2C%20but%20a%20sharp%20weapon%2C%20and%20we%20must%20fight%20to%20save%20Mumbai%20and%20the%20state.%20They%20must%20be%20given%20a%20befitting%20reply%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20those%20who%20split%20and%20left%20the%20party%20now%20want%20to%20return%20to%20the%20party%20fold%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20reiterated%20that%20those%20who%20want%20to%20leave%20can%20go%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20will%20continue%20the%20political%20fight%20with%20our%20Shiv%20Sainiks%20as%20our%20name%20has%20put%20fear%20in%20them%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%20also%20said%20that%20the%20dispute%20over%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20name%20and%20poll%20symbol%20--%20which%20were%20allotted%20to%20the%20group%20led%20by%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20--%20has%20created%20confusion%20among%20the%20people%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20will%20come%20in%20our%20favour%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20state%20President%20Chandrashekhar%20Bawankule%2C%20Ashish%20Shelar%2C%20Sudhir%20Mungantiwar%2C%20Pravin%20Darekar%2C%20Ashish%20Shelar%2C%20and%20others%2C%20lashed%20out%20at%20Mr%20Thackeray%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20%E2%80%9Csowing%20communal%20divisions%20among%20the%20people%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20saying%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20will%20have%20to%20take%20100%20births%20before%20finishing%20Mr%20Fadnavis'%20politics%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bawankule%20said%20Mr%20Thackeray%20has%20forgotten%20how%20he%20got%20his%20MPs%20elected%20in%20Narendra%20Modi's%20name%2C%20but%20when%20he%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%20backstabbed%20the%20BJP%20and%20even%20hatched%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20put%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20in%20jail%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20with%20people's%20blessings%2C%20he%20could%20not%20succeed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20BJP%20chief%20alleged%20Pakistani%20flags%20were%20seen%20in%20Mr%20Thackeray's%20meetings%20in%20Nashik%20and%20Mumbai%2C%20but%20now%20he's%20talking%20about%20finishing%20Mr%20Fadnavis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20accused%20Mr%20Thackeray%20of%20provoking%20such%20elements%20and%20polarising%20different%20castes%20and%20religions%20that%20have%20l