202024%2C%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%20will%20enforce%20new%20guidelines%20for%20FASTag%20users%2C%20focusing%20on%20updated%20Know%20Your%20Customer%20(KYC)%20requirements.%C2%A0FASTag%20is%20a%20pre-paid%20tag%20facility%20for%20vehicles%20that%20allows%20non-stop%20movement%20of%20traffic%20without%20having%20to%20wait%20at%20the%20toll%20plazas.%20The%20FASTag%20KYC%20check%20has%20been%20introduced%20to%20enhance%20the%20efficiency%20of%20the%20electronic%20toll%20collection%20system%20and%20provide%20seamless%20movement%20at%20toll%20plazas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20key%20changes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EKYC%20Update%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFASTag%20users%20must%20update%20their%20KYC%20details%20until%20October%2031%2C%20especially%20if%20their%20FASTag%20is%20between%203%20to%205%20years%20old%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EReplacement%20of%20Old%20FASTags%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Any%20FASTags%20older%20than%20five%20years%20must%20be%20replaced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELinking%20Vehicle%20Details%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EVehicle%20registration%20number%20and%20chassis%20number%20must%20be%20linked%20with%20the%20FASTag%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Vehicle%20Registration%20Update%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENew%20vehicle%20owners%20must%20update%20their%20FASTag%20with%20the%20vehicle's%20registration%20number%20within%2090%20days%20of%20purchase.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDatabase%20Verification%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20FASTag%20providers%20must%20verify%20their%20databases%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPhoto%20Upload%20Requirement%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20improve%20identification%20and%20security%2C%20FASTag%20providers%20are%20now%20required%20to%20upload%20clear%2C%20high-quality%20photos%20of%20the%20vehicle's%20front%20and%20side.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMobile%20Number%20Linking%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20ensure%20seamless%20communication%20and%20timely%20updates%2C%20it's%C2%A0mandatory%20to%20link%20each%20FASTag%20to%20a%20mobile%20number.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20FASTag%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFASTag%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20pre-paid%20tag%20facility%20for%20vehicles%20that%20uses%20technology%20to%20eliminate%20bottlenecks%20on%20toll%20plazas%20across%20India.%20Once%20the%C2%A0FASTag%C2%A0is%20active%2C%20it%20is%20affixed%20on%20the%20vehicle's%20windscreen%20and%20information%20on%20it%20is%20passively%20read%20by%20the%20antennae%20at%20the%20toll%20plaza%2C%20debiting%20the%20toll%20amount%20from%20one's%20bank%20account%20that%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20FASTag.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20penetration%20rate%20of%20around%2098%25%20and%20over%20eight%20crore%20users%2C%20FASTag%20has%20revolutionised%20the%20country's%20electronic%20toll%20collection%20system.%C2%A0It%20employs%20Radio%20Frequency%20Identification%20(RFID)%20technology%20for%20toll%20payments%20directly%20from%20the%20account%20linked%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsers%20can%20buy%20FASTags%20from%20toll%20plazas%2C%20petrol%20pumps%20of%20Indian%20Oil%2C%20Hindustan%20Petroleum%2C%20Bharat%20Petroleum%2C%20banks%2C%20PAYTM%20and%20Amazon.%20Using%20FASTag%20comes%20with%20several%20benefits.%20It%20provides%20uninterrupted%20traffic%20movement%2C%20helps%20save%20paper%2C%20reduces%20pollution%2C%20and%20traffic%20congestion%2C%20and%20is%20convenient%20and%20cashless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722445140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fg6fvprq8_fastag_625x300_16_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-fastag-rules-to-come-into-effect-on-august-1-check-details-6234049%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Under%20the%20new%20FASTag%20rules%2C%20Know%20Your%20Customer%20(KYC)%20must%20be%20completed%20by%20October%2031.%22%2C%22auth