s%2Fcdcb%2Flive%2F0da4ebb0-4ef9-11ef-94f6-4bf59678de16.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcd108y8439po%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%20192%20people%20are%20still%20missing%20after%20heavy%20rains%20triggered%20massive%20landslides%20in%20Kerala%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A263%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcd108y8439po%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcd108y8439po.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcd108y8439po.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20may%20have%20tortured%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20-%20UN%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722435531000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fbccf%2Flive%2Fea9cbde0-4f30-11ef-aebc-6de4d31bf5cd.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcglkvjr7lx0o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UN%20said%20a%20%26quot%3Bstaggering%20number%26quot%3B%20of%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20detained%20by%20Israel%2C%20with%20many%20facing%20torture%20and%20abuse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A65%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcglkvjr7lx0o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcglkvjr7lx0o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcglkvjr7lx0o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRemote%20Sensing%20Not%20Enough...%26quot%3B%3A%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20On%20Predicting%20Landslides%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20landslides%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20-%20which%20have%20killed%20at%20least%20150%20people%20and%20flattened%20villages%20-%20underline%20the%20importance%20of%20developing%20technology%20to%20predict%20such%20ecological%20disasters%20and%20give%20authorities%20time%20to%20evacuate%20people%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20told%20NDTV%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharoor%2C%20a%20multiple-term%20MP%20from%20Kerala%20capital%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20pointed%20to%20the%20southern%20state's%20ecologically%20fragile%20terrain%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20floods%20in%202017%20(due%20to%20Cyclone%20Ockhi)%2C%20and%202018%20and%202019%20too%2C%20and%20said%20the%20challenge%20is%20to%20predict%20such%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20hearing%20of%20over%20200%20deaths%20and%20500%20houses%20destroyed...%20and%20perhaps%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20more%20people%20trapped%20under%20debris.%20So%20it%20is%20really%20a%20very%20sad%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20predict%20(landslides)...%20because%20the%20fundamental%20reality%20we%20have%20to%20live%20with%20is%20that%20Kerala%20is%20ecologically%20very%20fragile.%20In%20the%20last%20few%20years%20alone%20we%20have%20had%20major%20challenges%2C%20including%20climate%20change.%20The%20devastation%20of%20Cyclone%20Ockhi%20in%202017%20and%20significant%20flooding%20in%202018%20and%202019...%20amid%20all%20of%20this%20there%20were%20landslides%20in%20Wayanad%20then%20too...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20as%20if%20we%20haven't%20seen%20this%20before...%20the%20challenge%20is%20how%20do%20we%20predict%20these%20so%20we%20can%20evacuate%20people%20before%20the%20worst.%20And%20that%20is%20something%20we%20surely%20ought%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20rely%20heavily%20on%20remote%20sensing...%20but%20experts%20are%20saying%20this%20is%20not%20enough%20and%20that%20we%20need%20to%20have%20sensor%20grids%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20be%20able%20to%20anticipate%20landslides.%20We%20don't%20have%20that...%20we%20don't%20have%20an%20on-ground%20sensor%20grid.%20We%20need%20more%20real-time%20data%20gathering...%26quot%3B%20he%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20should%20not%20be%20beyond%20the%20technological%20capacity%20of%20the%20country%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20is%20a%20mountainous%20state%20in%20which%20over%20half%20of%20the%20terrain%20consists%20of%20slopes%20exceeding%2020%20degrees%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20you%20can%20imagine%20how%20susceptible%20it%20is%20to%20soil%20erosion%20and%20landslides.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharoor%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20challenges%20of%20global%20warming%20and%20climate%20change.%20%26quot%3BDue%20to%20warming%20of%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%20there%20are%20deep%20cloud%20systems%20that%20release%20sudden%20and%20extensive%20rain%20over%20shorter%20periods...%20which%20means%20the%20soil%20gets%20saturated%20quickly%20and%20landslides%20result.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20forecast%20(for%20the%20landslide-hit%20areas%20in%20Wayanad)%20was%2062%20mm%20but%20they%20got%20322%20mm...%20now%20what%20do%20you%20do%20with%20that%20much%20rain%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20underline%20this%20unpredictability%2C%20he%20referred%20to%20the%20Gadgil%20Commission%20Report%20that%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20centre%20in%202011.%20It%20recommended%20large%20sections%20of%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20have%20'ecologically%20sensitive'%20zones%2C%20which%20would%20require%20re-settling%20existing%20human%20populations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%2C%20even%20that%20report%20failed%20to%20identify%20villages%20wiped%20out%20in%20these%20landslides%20as%20existing%20in%20ecologically%20fragile%20areas.%20And%20the%20complications%2C%20he%20said%2C%20didn't%20end%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharoor%20underlined%20the%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20difficulties%20of%20resettling%20people%2C%20including%20ensuring%20livelihoods%20were%20not%20affected%20or%2C%20if%20they%20were%2C%20to%20ensure%20they%20had%20access%20to%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20spat%20between%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Kerala%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20-%20about%20the%20centre's%20warnings%20to%20the%20state%20about%20potential%20landslides%20in%20the%20area%20-%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20keep%20politics%20apart%20from%20humanitarian%20issues%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20a%20blame%20game%20is%20where%20we%20should%20be%20going%20when%20lives%20are%20at%20stake%20and%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20rescue%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722435180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fs6qt16e8_wayanad-landslide_625x300_31_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwayanad-landslides-news-shashi-tharoor-remote-sensing-not-enough-shashi-tharoor-on-predicting-landslides-6232965%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20landslides%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20-%20which%20have%20killed%20at%20least%20150%20people%20-%20underline%20the%20importance%20of%20developing%20technology%20to%20predict%20such%20ecological%20disasters%20and%20give%20authorities%20time%20to%20evacuate%20people%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwayanad-landslides-news-shashi-tharoor-remote-sensing-not-enough-shashi-tharoor-on-predicting-landslides-6232965%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwayanad-landslides-news-shashi-tharoor-remote-sensing-not-enough-shashi-tharoor-on-predicting-landslides-6232965%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwayanad-landslides-news-shashi-tharoor-remote-sensing-not-enough-shashi-tharoor-on-predicting-landslides-6232965%2Famp%2F1%22%7D