a.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fgrandmother-run-businesses-4-1721885949-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fgrandmother-run-businesses-4-1721885949-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358448%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAmmiji%E2%80%99s%20was%20started%20by%20Rajinder%20Kaur%20Chatha%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20come%20up%20with%20authentic%20chai%20masala%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Amrita%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMemories%20of%20drinking%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20her%20home%20in%20Amritsar%20formed%20the%20bedrock%20against%20which%2096-year-old%20Rajinder%20Kaur%20Chatha%20started%20Ammiji%E2%80%99s.%20Recalling%20this%20anecdote%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20married%20in%201948%20and%20came%20to%20live%20with%20a%20stranger%2C%20in%20a%20strange%20house%2C%20and%20among%20slightly%20hostile%20strangers.%20In%20a%20world%20that%20was%20unfamiliar%20and%20sometimes%20heartbreakingly%20cruel%2C%20I%20sought%20comfort%2C%20which%20for%20me%20had%20always%20been%20%3Cem%3Echai%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20I%20hated%20the%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20that%20house.%20It%20was%20a%20mud-like%20concoction%2C%20thick%20with%20sugar%20and%20devoid%20of%20flavour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20on%20one%20of%20her%20trips%20to%20the%20spice%20bazaars%20of%20Amritsar%2C%20she%20bought%20a%20handful%20of%20spices%20and%20decided%20to%20concoct%20her%20own%20%3Cem%3Echai.%20%3C%2Fem%3EThis%20blended%20in%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F245061%2Fpunjab-startup-woman-entrepreneur-ammijis-chai-masala-homemade-spices-amritsar-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20mother%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Erecipe%20%3C%2Fa%3Eled%20to%20a%20creation%20that%20not%20j