0possibilities.%20Soon%2C%20she%20started%20competing%20in%20district%2C%20state%2C%20national%20and%20international%20level%20competitions%2C%20emerging%20victorious%20each%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntranced%20by%20the%20world%20of%20competitive%20sports%2C%20she%20then%20tried%20her%20hand%20at%20powerlifting%20and%20arm%20wrestling%20too.%20The%20result%20%E2%80%94%20just%20as%20you%20expected%20%E2%80%94%20earned%20her%20the%20title%20of%20%E2%80%98Iron%20Lady%20of%20Assam%E2%80%99%20at%20the%20state%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20incredibly%20proud%20of%20her.%20I%20remember%20the%20first%20time%20she%20won%20a%20competition%20in%20swimming.%20It%20was%20sometime%20in%202013-14%20and%20we%20threw%20a%20big%20party%20for%20her%20with%20all%20relatives%20and%20friends.%20They%20all%20were%20so%20proud%20of%20her%20and%20wanted%20her%20to%20continue%20and%20achieve%20bigger%20things.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20happiest%20I%20had%20ever%20seen%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20her%20son%20Anjumon%2C%20his%20voice%20brimming%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%E2%80%99ve%20always%20heard%20parents%20speak%20about%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20achievements.%20It%E2%80%99s%20pleasantly%20surprising%20when%20the%20tables%20are%20turned%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%2062-year-old%20Ranjita%E2%80%99s%20inspiring%20tale%20of%20achieving%20her%20dreams%2C%20age%20no%20bar!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20down%20a%20government%20job%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20a%20Bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20(BSc)%20in%20agriculture%2C%20Ranjita%20got%20a%20government%20job.%20Post%20marriage%2C%20she%20shifted%20to%20a%20nearby%20district%20of%20Jorhat%2C%20where%20she%20continued%20her%20service.%20She%20then%20moved%20to%20the%20Philippines%20for%20a%20few%20years%20for%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20PhD%20degree.%20Always%20eager%20to%20learn%2C%20she%20pursued%20a%20course%20in