hing%20it%20post%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Sachin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20started%20with%20practical%20subjects%20like%20Financial%20Reporting%20(FR)%2C%20Strategic%20Financial%20Management%20(SFM)%2C%20and%20Advanced%20Management%20Accounting%2C%20as%20they%20take%20the%20most%20amount%20of%20time%20and%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20conceptual%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeekends%20for%20these%20teenagers%20involved%20%E2%80%98no%20fun%E2%80%99.%20They%20were%20devoted%20to%20watching%20lectures%20and%20self-study.%20In%20fact%2C%20Nandini%20calls%20her%20CA%20journey%20the%20most%20beautiful%20part%20of%20her%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20their%20CA%20Final%20attempt%20in%20May%202021%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288421%2Fca-ishu-agrawal-shares-tips-on-how-he-cleared-upsc-cse-while-working%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esiblings%20started%20intense%20preparations%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20December%2C%20when%20their%20study%20leave%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20motivated%20each%20other%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20study%20plan%20was%20target-based%2C%20not%20time-based.%20They%20would%20decide%20what%20they%20had%20to%20complete%20each%20day.%20They%20first%20completed%20all%20pending%20lectures%20when%20their%20study%20leave%20started.%20The%20first%20subject%20they%20picked%20up%20in%20December%20was%20taxation.%20Their%20plan%20was%20divided%20into%2015-day%20chunks%2C%20each%20covering%20one%20practical%20and%20one%20theory%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nandini%20and%20Sachin%20coached%20and%20motivated%20each%20other%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358959%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENandini%20and%20Sachin%20coached%20and%20motivated%20each%20other%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20exam%20had%20eight%20subjects%20at%20that%20time%2C%20they%20completed%20their%20first%20revision%20in%20two%20months.%20They%20referred%20to%20The%20Institute%20of%20Chartered%20Accountants%20of%20India%20(ICAI)%20modules%20and%20past%20papers%2C%20and%20took%20some%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20revision%20included%20trying%20to%20solve%20past%20papers%2C%20which%20gave%20them%20an%20idea%20about%20which%20areas%20needed%20more%20focus.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20targeted%2010%20days%20for%20two%20subjects%20in%20this%20revision%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sachin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%2C%20they%20attempted%20some%20mock%20test%20papers%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20March.%20The%20results%20were%20shocking%2C%20says%20Sachin.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20failed%20in%20a%20few%20papers.%20Even%20in%20other%20subjects%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20the%20result%20we%20wanted.%20We%20were%20shattered%20to%20see%20the%20result%20after%20all%20our%20hard%20work.%20This%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20enough%20to%20secure%20a%20rank%2C%20which%20was%20our%20aim%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E