industry%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSTIs%20have%20a%20meticulously%20designed%20curriculum%20that%20caters%20to%20both%20newcomers%20and%20the%20less%20experienced%20segments%20of%20the%20workforce%2C%20progressively%20enhancing%20their%20expertise%20across%20various%20construction%20trades.%20The%20courses%20are%20tailored%20to%20underprivileged%20individuals%20from%20marginalised%20backgrounds%2C%20aged%2018%20to%2035%2C%20who%20have%20passed%20Class%205.%20Trainees%20are%20selected%20through%20a%20process%20that%20includes%20an%20entrance%20test%20(both%20written%20and%20practical)%20and%20a%20viva%20voce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSTIs%20offer%20a%20variety%20of%20courses%20tailored%20to%20the%20construction%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20including%20formwork%20carpentry%2C%20bar%20bending%2C%20steel%20fixing%2C%20masonry%20(brickwork%20and%20block%20work)%2C%20plumbing%2C%20sanitary%2C%20electrical%20work%2C%20scaffolding%2C%20welding%2C%20tiling%2C%20and%20pipe%20welding.%20They%20also%20include%20courses%20related%20to%20smart%20city%20projects%2C%20such%20as%20optical%20fibre%20cable%20(OFC)%20and%20CCTV%20Installation%2C%20solar%20panel%20installation%2C%20and%20metro%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-2-1722003002.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20CSTIs%20offer%20a%20variety%20of%20courses%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-2-1722003002.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-2-1722003002-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-2-1722003002-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-2-1722003002-768x512.jpeg%20768w%