2051000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FLT-1722002541.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358777%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20(L%26amp%3BT)%E2%80%99s%20Construction%20Skills%20Training%20Institutes%20(CSTIs)%20provide%20vocational%20training%20to%20underprivileged%20rural%20youth%2C%20equipping%20them%20with%20essential%20skills%20for%20the%20construction%20sector.%20These%20institutes%20have%20helped%20many%20secure%20employment%20with%20top%20construction%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A232%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98My%20Disability%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Limit%20My%20Service%E2%80%99%3A%20Visually-Impaired%20Civil%20Servant%20On%20UPSC%20Disability%20Quota%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20selection%20of%20Puja%20Khedkar%2C%20the%20trainee%20IAS%20(Indian%20Administrative%20Service)%20officer%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20cadre%2C%20who%20allegedly%20availed%20of%20concessions%20for%20physical%20disability%20and%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes%20reservations)%2C%20has%20sparked%20a%20furious%20debate%20online%20on%20reservations%20for%20the%20disabled%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20elite%20civil%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20various%20revelations%20of%20alleged%20impropriety%20in%20the%20media%2C%20her%20two-year%20training%20has%20been%20put%20on%20hold%2C%20and%20her%20selection%20into%20the%20IAS%20is%20now%20being%20probed%20by%20a%20panel%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Union%20Government.%20What%20this%20decision%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20done%20is%20lessen%20the%20volume%20of%20those%20questioning%20the%20need%20for%20a%20disability%20quota%20in%20the%20elite%20civil%20services%20given%20their%20concerns%20of%20%E2%80%98misuse%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Constitution%20guarantees%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341616%2Fbest-books-on-disability-inclusivity-mental-health-stigma-sign-language-books%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eequal%20rights%20and%20opportunities%20for%20the%20disabled%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recognising%20those%20persons%20with%2040%25%20or%20more%20disability%20certified%20by%20medical%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20everything%20from%20hearing%20impairment%20to%20visual%20impairment%2C%20blindness%2C%20and%20locomotive%20disabilities.%20Under%20the%20Disability%20Discrimination%20Act%2C%201995%2C%20a%203%25%20reservation%20is%20provided%20for%20the%20disabled.%20This%20law%20was%20replaced%20by%20the%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%2C%202016%2C%20which%20increases%20reservations%20to%204%25%20for%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(PwD)%20in%20various%20sectors%2C%20including%20those%20attempting%20the%20UPSC%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20(CSE).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20senior%20IAS%20officer%20of%20Telangana%20cadre%2C%20Smita%20Sabharwal%2C%20wrote%20a%20post%20on%20X%20questioning%20the%20provision%20of%20reservations%20for%20disabled%20persons%20in%20the%20civil%20services.%20She%20posed%20on%20X%3A%20%E2%80%9CWith%20all%20due%20respect%20to%20the%20Differently%20Abled.%20Does%20an%20Airline%20hire%20a%20pilot%20with%20%5Ba%5D%20disability%3F%20Or%20would%20you%20trust%20a%20surgeon%20with%20a%20disability.%20The%20nature%20of%20the%20%23AIS%20(IAS%2FIPS%2FIFoS)%20is%20field-work%2C%20long%20taxing%20hours%2C%20listening%20first%20hand%20to%20people%E2%80%99s%20grievances-which%20requires%20physical%20fitness.%20Why%20does%20this%20premier%20service%20need%20this%20Quota%20in%20the%20first%20place!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20Amitabh%20Kant%2C%20an%20ex-civil%20servant%20and%20former%20CEO%20of%20NITI%20Aayog%2C%20sought%20a%20review%20of%20the%20disability%20quota.%20He%20posted%20on%20X%3A%20%E2%80%9CSeveral%20cases%20of%20fraud%20through%20UPSC%20for%20entry%20to%20top%20Civil%20Services%20are%20being%20alleged.%20All%20such%20cases%20must%20be%20fully%20investigated%20and%20the%20sternest%20action%20taken.%20Selection%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20competence%20and%20integrity%20should%20never%20get%20compromised.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20in%20favour%20of%20SC%2FST%20and%20OBC%20reservation.%20These%20reservations%20should%20continue%2C%20with%20the%20Creamy%20layer%20regulations%20being%20enforced.%20However%2C%20the%20existing%20reservations%20for%20the%20physically%20and%20mentally%20handicapped%20and%20the%20proposed%201%25%20reservations%20for%20the%20third%20gender%20for%20the%20top%20Civil%20Services%20need%20to%20be%20reviewed.%20They%20are%20being%20misused%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20trustee%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fncpedp_india%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ncpedp_india%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20see%20thousands%20of%20innovative%20outcomes%20by%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20which%20is%20inspirational%20in%20many%20ways.%20NCPEDP%20was%20instrumental%20in%20getting%20disabled%20people%20in%20UPSC%20%26amp%3B%20we%20see%20them%20struggling%20daily%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20awareness.%20If%20given%20a%20universal%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FM6TUgDSIUY%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FM6TUgDSIUY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Arvind%20Gupta%20(%40buzzindelhi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbuzzindelhi%2Fstatus%2F1814941451001999420%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20need%20disability%20quota%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F178902%2Fupsc-result-topper-tips-farmer-son-ias-inspiring-india%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESatender%20Singh%20Pannu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20visually-impaired%20civil%20servant%20who%20is%20currently%20undergoing%20training%20at%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Training%20(Union%20Territories%20Civil%20Services)%2C%20says%20that%20the%20arguments%20that%20question%20the%20need%20for%20a%20disability%20quota%20are%20misplaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20opinions%2C%20he%20argues%2C%20have%20four%20profoundly%20disturbing%20problems%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20They%E2%80%99re%20ableist%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20denial%20of%20enabling%20conditions%20and%20affirmative%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20These%20views%20go%20against%20constitutional%20guarantees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4)%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20denial%20of%20social%20justice%20and%20the%20principle%20of%20reasonable%20accommodation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20first%20point%2C%20Satender%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20opinions%20exhibit%20an%20ableist%20point%20of%20view%2C%20which%20believes%20that%20people%20with%20disability%20are%20incompetent%20and%20incapable%20of%20performing%20the%20tasks%20that%20they%20are%20supposed%20to%20perform%20as%20IAS%20officers.%20But%20there%20are%20civil%20servants%20availing%20of%20the%20disability%20quota%20who%20have%20done%20better%20than%20their%20%E2%80%98able-bodied%E2%80%99%20peers%20in%20their%20various%20revenue%20postings.%20As%20DMs%20or%20SDMs%2C%20they%20have%20shown%20to%20be%20more%20than%20capable%20of%20going%20on%20field%20visits%2C%20listening%20to%20public%20grievances%20and%20fulfilling%20all%20other%20tasks%20expected%20of%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20his%20own%20experience%2C%20Satender%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CAffirmative%20action%20has%20definitely%20acted%20as%20an%20enabler.%20As%20a%20civil%20servant%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20in%20different%20roles.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20perception%20that%20a%20person%20with%20a%20visual%20disability%20will%20struggle%20to%20work%20as%20an%20effective%20officer%2C%20which%20is%20absolutely%20untrue.%20Seldom%20do%20people%20know%20the%20role%20of%20technology%20like%20screen%20reading%20software%2C%20text-to-speech%20technologies%2C%20and%20text%20reading%20technologies%2C%20which%20can%20even%20read%20handwriting%2C%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20to%20assist%20officers%20like%20us.%20These%20technologies%20and%20my%20own%20slight%20adjustments%20and%20adaptations%20have%20ensured%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20as%20competent%20as%20anybody%20else.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20second%20point%2C%20he%20also%20believes%20that%20such%20arguments%20also%20reflect%20the%20denial%20of%20enabling%20conditions%20and%20the%20project%20of%20social%20inclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDisability%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20stamina%20or%20competence.%20For%20people%20from%20excluded%20communities%2C%20what%20matters%20is%20the%20provision%20of%20conditions%20that%20will%20enable%20them%20to%20thrive.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295507%2Fdisability-inclusive-policy-at-workplaces-lessons-from-accenture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWe%20need%20enabling%20conditions%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20overcome%20caste%2C%20class%20and%20other%20such%20social%20constructs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20strive%20to%20eradicate%20caste%20through%20affirmative%20action.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20need%20enabling%20conditions%20for%20the%20disabled%20so%20that%20society%20can%20step%20out%20of%20its%20ableist%20mentality.%20They%20should%20not%20be%20excluded%20from%20service%20just%20because%20they%20happen%20to%20be%20victims%20of%20social%20structures%2C%20prejudicial%20benefits%20and%20inaccessible%20attitudes.%20We%20need%20to%20be%20provided%20with%20attitudinal%2C%20structural%20and%20institutional%20accessibility%20for%20us%20to%20perform%20our%20role%20as%20officers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-2-1722004219.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22UPSC%20exam%20gives%20disability%20quota%20for%20IAS%20officers%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-2-1722004219.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-2-1722004219-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-2-1722004219-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-2-1722004219-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-2-1722004219-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358813%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Disability%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20stamina%20or%20competence%E2%80%99%20(For%20representational%20purposes%20only)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatender%20also%20believes%20that%20the%20real%20issue%20is%20being%20lost%20amidst%20all%20the%20noise%20surrounding%20the%20Puja%20Khedkar%20controversy.%20As%20he%20argues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20distraction%20from%20the%20real%20issue.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20about%20scrapping%20affirmative%20action%20for%20the%20disabled.%20The%20real%20issue%20is%20to%20implement%20it%20properly.%20Reservation%20has%20not%20been%20implemented%20in%20its%20true%20spirit%2C%20and%20now%20we%20have%20forgery%2C%20deception%20and%20fake%20certificates%20that%20eat%20into%20it.%20This%20should%20be%20talked%20about%20and%20rectified.%20We%20should%20not%20throw%20the%20baby%20out%20with%20the%20bathwater.%20Everyone%20deserves%20a%20chance%20to%20live%20with%20dignity%2C%20including%20a%20disabled%20person%2C%20and%20this%20is%20their%20constitutional%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20committed%20to%20providing%20the%20disabled%20with%20all%20the%20rights%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(RPWD)%20Act%2C%202016%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Convention%20on%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(UNCRPD)%2C%20and%20other%20such%20covenants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20should%20exclude%20someone%20from%20a%20responsibility%20they%E2%80%99re%20competent%20to%20execute%20if%20they%20satisfy%20all%20the%20required%20conditions.%20People%20who%20have%20availed%20of%20the%20disability%20quota%20have%20cleared%20the%20civil%20service%20examinations%20(CSE).%20They%20have%20cleared%20the%20same%20exam%20as%20able-bodied%20people%20who%20are%20talking%20about%20scrapping%20reservations%20for%20the%20elite%20service.%20Scrapping%20something%20like%20the%20disability%20quota%20goes%20against%20their%20rights%2C%20dignity%2C%20and%20social%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20on%20the%20fourth%20point%2C%20Satender%20argues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20note%20that%20we%20have%20already%20identified%20services%20in%20which%20people%20with%20disabilities%20can%20perform%20well%2C%20and%20the%20IAS%20is%20one%20of%20them.%20This%20has%20been%20done%20following%20the%20principle%20of%20reasonable%20accommodation.%20We%20have%20not%20identified%20flying%20an%20aeroplane%20or%20the%20responsibility%20of%20an%20IPS%20officer%20for%20the%20visually%20impaired.%20The%20roles%20that%20have%20already%20been%20identified%20and%20considered%20suitable%20for%20visually%20impaired%20persons%20should%20not%20be%20denied%20to%20them%2C%20in%20which%20they%20have%20already%20established%20themselves.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDo%20we%20need%20a%20review%20of%20the%20disability%20quota%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatender%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20that%20we%20need%20to%20review%20the%20reservation%20quota%20for%20the%20disabled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20because%20some%20facility%20is%20being%20encroached%20upon%2C%20you%20do%20not%20end%20it.%20You%20punish%20the%20encroachers%20and%20proactively%20plug%20the%20loopholes%20to%20allow%20genuine%20candidates%20to%20use%20the%20facility.%20Reservation%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%20needs%20to%20be%20implemented%20in%20its%20true%20spirit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20former%20decorated%20IAS%20officer%20who%20also%20availed%20of%20the%20disability%20quota%20but%20wishes%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20actually%20shocked%20that%20she%20%5BPuja%20Khedkar%5D%20could%20bypass%20all%20the%20checks.%20I%20am%20actually%20puzzled%20how%20these%20people%20can%20actually%20get%20through%20it.%20The%20vetting%20process%20for%20candidates%20availing%20the%20disability%20quota%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20stringent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20720px)%20100vw%2C%20720px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFB_IMG_1722001043015-1722003789.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Disability%20Quota%20UPSC%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFB_IMG_1722001043015-1722003789.jpg%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFB_IMG_1722001043015-172200378