22_blank%5C%22%3ERigzin%20Samphel%3C%2Fa%3E%20(UP%20cadre)%20and%20DS%20Lokesh%20Kumar%20(Telangana%20cadre)%20who%20had%20to%20file%20a%20case%20in%20a%20court%20before%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20(PMO)%20intervened%20on%20their%20behalf%20to%20get%20their%20preferred%20service%20(IAS)%20allotted%20to%20them.%20Samphel%2C%20a%202003-batch%20officer%20with%20All%20India%20Rank%20(AIR)%20120%20and%20AIR%202%20(Scheduled%20Tribe)%2C%20was%20also%20eligible%20for%20the%20disability%20quota%20(locomotor)%20given%20his%20severely%20damaged%20right%20leg.%20Lokesh%20was%20eligible%20for%20the%20same%20quota%20after%20contracting%20polio%20on%20one%20leg%20at%20a%20young%20age.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20virtue%20of%20being%20an%20ST%20(Scheduled%20Tribe)%20candidate%2C%20Samphel%20should%20have%20been%20given%20the%20IAS%20since%20that%20year%20there%20were%20six%20seats%20available%20for%20ST%20category%20candidates.%20Even%20if%20he%20was%20denied%20all%20reservation%20quotas%2C%20the%20Government%20should%20have%20inducted%20him%20into%20the%20IRS%20since%20he%20had%20finished%20AIR%20120%20(General%20category).%20Instead%2C%20he%20was%20allotted%20the%20Indian%20Information%20Service%20(IIS)%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20(DoPT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20(DoPT)%20reasoning%20was%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20promote%20disabled%20people%20in%20the%20services%2C%20and%20there%20were%20seats%20specifically%20reserved%20for%20them%20in%20the%20IIS%20but%20not%20the%20IAS.%20In%20response%2C%20Samphel%20and%20Lokesh%20told%20the%20DoPT%20that%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20reservation%20under%20the%20disability%20quota%20and%20that%20they%20should%20have%20been%20allocated%20the%20IAS%20by%20virtue%20of%20their%20performance%20in%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-1722004133.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Disability%20quota%20in%20the%20IAS%20via%20the%20UPSC%20exam%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-1722004133.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-1722004133-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-1722004133-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-1722004133-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-1722004133-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358811%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20representational%20purposes%20only%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELokesh%2C%20AIR%20122%20and%20AIR%206%20(Scheduled%20Caste)%2C%20was%20eligible%20for%20IAS%20since%20that%20year%2C%20there%20were%20eight%20seats%20available%20for%20SC%20category%20candidates.%20Hurt%20by%20this%20injustice%2C%20Samphel%20and%20Lokesh%20filed%20a%20case%20in%202003%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20saying%20they%20did%20not%20want%20the%20benefit%20of%20reservation%20under%20the%20disability%20quota%20because%20it%20was%20being%20used%20against%20their%20interest.%20By%20virtue%20of%20their%20own%20merit%2C%20they%20were%20getting%20into%20the%20service%20of%20their%20choice%20(IAS)%2C%20but%20the%20rules%20listed%20in%20the%20Disability%20Act%2C%201995%2C%20were%20being%20used%20in%20an%20%E2%80%98illogical%20manner%E2%80%99%20to%20deny%20them%20entry%20into%20the%20IAS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20their%20case%2C%20however%2C%20there%20was%20a%20separate%20PIL%20(public%20interest%20litigation)%20filed%20by%20two%20judges%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20who%20happened%20to%20read%20about%20their%20case%20in%20the%20media.%20Concurrently%2C%20Samphel%20and%20Lokesh%20went%20about%20pursuing%20their%20own%20case%20through%20the%20then%20Ladakh%20MP%20Thupstan%20Chhewang%20and%20they%20approached%20the%20PMO%20for%20their%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20luck%20would%20have%20it%2C%20the%20PMO%20was%20benevolent%20towards%20their%20cause%20and%20ordered%20a%20second%20medical%20examination%20to%20see%20whether%20they%20were%20fit%20to%20serve%20in%20the%20IAS%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DoPT%20reconstituted%20a%20medical%20board%20in%202004%20to%20assess%20whether%20they%20were%20capable%20of%20carrying%20out%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20IAS%20in%20terms%20of%20physical%20fitness.%20After%20putting%20Samphel%20and%20Lokesh%20through%20various%20tests%2C%20they%20decided%20that%20both%20of%20them%20were%20fit%20for%20all%20non-technical%20services%20and%20therefore%20should%20be%20inducted%20into%20the%20IAS.%20From%20the%20time%20they%20had%20filed%20the%20case%20till%20its%20resolution%2C%20they%20were%20serving%20as%20probationers%20in%20the%20IIS%2C%20partially%20under%20duress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20resolution%2C%20there%20was%20another%20PIL%20filed%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20as%20stated%20earlier.%20This%20PIL%20snowballed%20into%20many%20questions%20from%20the%20court%20about%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20position%20on%20disabled%20candidates%20serving%20in%20the%20elite%20services.%20Finally%2C%20in%202005%2C%20the%20DoPT%20issued%20a%20circular%20saying%20that%20seats%20would%20be%20reserved%20for%20disabled%20people%20in%20the%20IAS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Samphel%20and%20Lokesh%20have%20built%20stellar%20careers%20in%20the%20service%20with%20the%20former%20taking%20voluntary%20retirement%20last%20year.%20Their%20%E2%80%98disability%E2%80%99%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20their%20ability%20to%20serve.%20Despite%20the%20examples%20they%E2%80%99ve%20set%2C%20the%20system%20seems%20determined%20to%20keep%20deserving%20disabled%20candidates%20out%20of%20the%20higher%20echelons%20of%20the%20Indian%20bureaucracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20must%20read%20inspiring%20journey%20of%20a%20differently-abled%20IAS%20officer%20of%20Telangana%20cadre%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20the%20year%202003%2C%20a%20UPSC%20AIS%20aspirant%20worked%20hard%20%26amp%3B%20secured%20a%20good%20rank%20.%20But%20instead%20of%20IAS%20posting%2C%20he%20was%20given%20IIS%20posting%20because%20of%20his%20disability.%20There%20were%202others%20along%20with%20him%2C%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5O6iUPzO1K%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5O6iUPzO1K%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Naveena%20(%40TheNaveena)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheNaveena%2Fstatus%2F1815690240603893924%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20example%20of%20Ira%20Singhal%2C%20a%202015-batch%20IAS%20officer%20with%20hyperkyphosis%20scoliosis%2C%20a%20spine-related%20disorder%2C%20who%20topped%20the%20civil%20service%20examinations%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20prior%20to%20this%20phenomenal%20achievement%2C%20she%20had%20scored%20enough%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20IRS%2C%20but%20her%20appointment%20was%20cancelled%20with%20the%20Government%20citing%20her%20disability%20as%20a%20reason.%20She%20then%20sought%20legal%20intervention%20from%20the%20Central%20Administrative%20Tribunal%20(CAT).%20Just%20as%20she%20was%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20appearing%20for%20her%20second%20attempt%2C%20she%20received%20her%20letter%20of%20appointment%20but%20still%20went%20ahead%20with%20writing%20the%20exam%20and%20came%20back%20much%20stronger%2C%20according%20to%20an%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20you%20have%20the%20case%20of%20ISRO%20scientist%20Kartik%20Kansal%2C%20who%20suffers%20from%20muscular%20dystrophy%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20has%20been%20confined%20to%20a%20wheelchair%20since%20he%20was%2014.%20Despite%20clearing%20the%20UPSC%20exam%20four%20times%2C%20he%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20allocated%20a%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Masterminds%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%20far%2C%20Kartik%20has%20made%20a%20total%20of%20six%20attempts%20at%20the%20UPSC%20exam%2C%20successfully%20clearing%20it%20four%20times.%20His%20All%20India%20Rank%20(AIR)%20was%20813%20in%202019%2C%20improved%20to%20271%20in%202021%20(his%20best%20rank%20so%20far)%2C%20followed%20by%20784%20in%20UPSC-2022%2C%20and%20829%20in%20UPSC-2023.%20Despite%20these%20achievements%2C%20he%20has%20not%20been%20allocated%20a%20service%20in%20three%20of%20his%20successful%20attempts%2C%20and%20for%20the%20fourth%20attempt%20in%202023%2C%20service%20allocation%20is%20pending.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20case%20is%20currently%20pending%20before%20CAT%20based%20on%20his%202021%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20DoPT%2C%20the%20%5B2021%5D%20notification%20specifies%20muscular%20dystrophy%20as%20an%20eligible%20condition%20for%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20in%20the%20IRS%20service%20category.%20However%2C%20Kartik%E2%80%99s%20condition%2C%20affecting%20both%20legs%20and%20both%20arms%20(known%20as%20Primary%20Lateral%20Sclerosis%20or%20PLS)%2C%20is%20categorised%20differently%20and%20is%20recognised%20under%20IAS%20but%20not%20under%20IRS%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20the%20DoPT%20argues%20that%20since%20the%20IRS%20does%20not%20include%20a%20category%20specifically%20for%20both%20legs%20and%20both%20arms%20disability%2C%20Kartik%20cannot%20be%20allocated%20this%20service%20despite%20his%20qualification%20under%20the%20broader%20disability%20category%20of%20muscular%20dystrophy.%20Kartik%20cannot%20be%20allotted%20the%20IRS%20service%20due%20to%20this%20mismatch%20in%20disability%20category%20specification%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKartik%20met%20all%20the%20physical%20requirements%20to%20get%20into%20the%20IRS.%20But%20he%20fell%20afoul%20of%20a%20technicality%2C%20which%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20conform%20with%20logic.%20Why%20should%20his%20condition%20be%20recognised%20under%20the%20IAS%20but%20not%20the%20IRS%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20tough%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20this%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20we%20are%20left%20with%20a%20situation%20where%20candidates%20allegedly%20engaging%20in%20forgery%20and%20deception%20are%20availing%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20disability%20quota%20whereas%20deserving%20ones%20are%20getting%20left%20out%20in%20the%20cold.%20Maybe%2C%20instead%20of%20wanting%20to%20scrap%20or%20thoroughly%20review%20the%20requirement%20for%20it%2C%20the%20system%20would%20be%20better%20placed%20to%20hold%20its%20examiners%20more%20accountable%20and%20fix%20the%20loopholes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Satender%20Singh%20and%20Shutterstock)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAdditional%20Sources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianmasterminds.com%2Ffeatures%2Fdisability-vs-rules-how-kartik-kansals-upsc-saga-sparks-national-debate-91126%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisability%20vs.%20Rules%3A%20How%20Kartik%20Kansal%E2%80%99s%20UPSC%20Saga%20Sparks%20National%20Debate%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20by%20Ayodhya%20Prasad%20Singh%3B%20Published%20on%2020%20July%202024%20courtesy%20Indian%20Masterminds%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20171102083755%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Findiatoday.intoday.in%2Feducation%2Fstory%2Fias-topper-interview%2F1%2F663575.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFirst%20physically%20challenged%20woman%20to%20top%20IAS%2C%20Ira%20Singhal%20tells%20how%20her%20disability%20was%20never%20an%20excuse%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20by%20Ayushi%20Anand%3B%20Published%20on%209%20May%202016%20courtesy%20India%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722006442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUPSC-Disability-Quota-2-1722004219.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358800%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20controversy%20surrounding%20IAS%20trainee%20Puja%20Khedkar's%20selection%2C%20due%20to%5Cnalleged%20misuse%20of%20disability%20and%20OBC%20concessions%2C%20has%20reignited%20debates%20on%20reservations%20for%20disabled%20persons%20in%20India's%20civil%20services.%20Officers%20share%20their%20views.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358800%2Fupsc-cse-ias-irs-disability-quota-reservation-puja-khedkar-controversy-civil-servants-opinions%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Battling%20Bullying%20%26amp%3B%20Bias%2C%20These%20Women%20Wrestlers%E2%80%99%20Journey%20to%20Paris%20Olympics%20Is%20Forged%20in%20Grit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mahavir%20Phogat%20saw%20weightlifter%20Karnam%20Malleswari%E2%80%99s%20podium%20finish%20at%20the%202000%20Sydney%20Olympics%2C%20it%20inspired%20him%20to%20introduce%20the%20girls%20in%20his%20family%20to%20wrestling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20that%2C%20his%20aim%20was%20to%20prepare%20them%20for%20the%20Olympic%20podium.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20task%20in%20a%20state%20like%20Haryana%20with%20the%20lowest%20sex%20ratio%2C%20where%20women%E2%80%99s%20struggles%20begin%20in%20the%20womb%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20had%20been%20introduced%20in%20India%20in%20the%20mid-90s%2C%20it%20was%20largely%20confined%20to%20Delhi%20and%20had%20yet%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20Haryana.%20Mahavir%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20to%20train%20his%20daughters%20Geeta%2C%20Babita%2C%20Ritu%2C%20Sangeeta%2C%20along%20with%20his%20nieces%2C%20Vinesh%20and%20Priyanka%2C%20faced%20resistance%20from%20villagers%2C%20including%20his%20own%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20life%20inspired%20the%20Aamir%20Khan-starrer%20Bollywood%20movie%2C%20Dangal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllowing%20the%20girls%20to%20enter%20the%20mud%20pit%2C%20traditionally%20seen%20as%20a%20male%20domain%2C%20was%20met%20with%20significant%20opposition%20in%20his%20village%20Balali%20in%20Charkhi%20Dadri%20district%20(then%20in%20Bhiwani).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20almost%20a%20year-and-a-half%20later%2C%20an%20initiative%20to%20allow%20girls%20to%20train%20alongside%20boys%20at%20Chotu%20Ram%20Stadium%20Wrestling%20Centre%20in%20Rohtak%20faced%20societal%20hurdles.%20Former%20wrestlers%2C%20and%20even%20some%20coaches%2C%20expressed%20reservations%2C%20questioning%20%E2%80%9Chow%20goats%20could%20stay%20among%20the%20lions%E2%80%9D%2C%20fearing%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20girls%20would%20distract%20boys%2C%20leading%20to%20indiscipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%202024.%20What%20was%20once%20met%20with%20sarcasm%E2%80%94people%20comparing%20girls%20to%20goats%20and%20boys%20to%20lions%2C%20emphasising%20the%20perceived%20disparity%20in%20strength%20and%20prowess%20in%20the%20wrestling%20arena%E2%80%94has%20now%20become%20a%20point%20of%20pride.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%E2%80%99s%20women%20wrestlers%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20flag%20bearers%20of%20Indian%20wrestling%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20At%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Ffarmers-daughter-set-to-rock-paris-olympics-archery-shorts-parisolympics2024-sports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20Paris%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%20is%20represented%20by%20six%20wrestlers%2C%20five%20of%20whom%20are%20women%20from%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20rural%20landscape%2C%20where%20they%20once%20faced%20stiff%20opposition%20to%20entering%20the%20male-dominated%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMeet%20the%20team%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20wrestling%20contingent%20in%20Paris%20comprises%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20(50kg)%20from%20Charkhi%20Dadri%2C%20Antim%20Panghal%20(53kg)%20from%20Hisar%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263525%2Fanshu-malik-first-indian-woman-world-wrestling-championship-winner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Anshu%20Malik%20(57kg)%20from%20Jind%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nisha%20Dahiya%20(68kg)%20from%20Panipat%2C%20Reetika%20Hooda%20(76kg)%20from%20Rohtak%2C%20along%20with%20the%20lone%20male%20wrestler%2C%20Aman%20Sehrawat%20(57kg)%20from%20Jhajjar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COlympics%20is%20every%20sportsperson%E2%80%99s%20dream%2C%20and%20I%20am%20feeling%20happy%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20sporting%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Reetika%20Hooda%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Kharkara%20Village%20in%20Rohtak.%20%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20leading%20the%20Indian%20charge%20in%20Paris%20is%20a%20great%20motivation%20for%20its%20future%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Olympics%20at%20the%202004%20Athens%20Games%2C%20and%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20made%20their%20debut%20at%20the%202012%20London%20Olympics.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20Phogat%20f