a.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469-768x1023.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358785%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Phogat%20sisters.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202010%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20hosted%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20saw%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20making%20its%20debut%20in%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20and%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%E2%80%94three%20gold%2C%20two%20silver%2C%20and%20a%20bronze%E2%80%94changed%20society%E2%80%99s%20mindset%20towards%20women%20wrestlers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20no%20longer%20recognize%20them%20as%20goats%20but%20have%20started%20seeing%20them%20as%20lionesses%20in%20the%20wrestling%20arena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20long%20journey%2C%20from%20villagers%20being%20up%20in%20arms%20against%20the%20move%20of%20making%20the%20girls%20slug%20it%20out%20with%20boys%20in%20the%20mud%20pit%2C%20to%20the%20entire%20village%20standing%20in%20their%20honour%20for%20the%20women%20wrestlers%20winning%20medals%20at%20the%202010%20Commonwealth%20Games.%20Since%20then%2C%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20have%20excelled%20on%20the%20world%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mahavir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20five%20of%20them%20making%20it%20to%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20speaks%20a%20lot%20about%20women%20wrestling%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202016%20Rio%20Olympics%2C%20an%20edition%20after%20the%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20made%20their%20Olympic%20debut%2C%20a%20trainee%20of%20Rohtak%E2%80%99s%20Chotu%20Ram%20Wrestling%20Centre%2C%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20medal.%20She%20won%20bronze%20in%20Rio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20women%20trainees%20of%20the%20centre%20have%20had%20a%20presence%20in%20every%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%20Tokyo%2C%20Seema%20Bisla%2C%20who%20trained%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20wrestling%20contingent.%20Now%2C%20in%202024%20Paris%2C%20the%20centre%20is%20represented%20through%20its%20trainee%20Reetika%20Hooda%2C%20who%20is%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20in%20the%20heavyweight%20category%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImmediately%20after%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20was%20introduced%20in%20Haryana%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20girls%20began%20making%20their%20presence%20felt%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20and%20gradually%20the%20Indian%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20squad%20became%20largely%20an%20all-Haryana%20affair%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Mandeep%2C%20a%20coach%20at%20the%20centre%20under%20whom%20Sakshi%20Malik%20and%20Reetika%20train.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20the%20women%20wrestlers%20from%20Haryana%20have%20become%20synonymous%20with%20Indian%20wrestling.%20It%20feels%20nice%20that%20you%20have%20contributed%20your%20bit%20to%20this%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20has%20seen%20a%20vertical%20growth.%20A%20decade%20ago%2C%20there%20were%20around%2020%20girls%20at%20the%20Rohtak%20centre%2C%20and%20now%20the%20number%20has%20crossed%20100.%20And%20I%20am%20only%20talking%20about%20one%20training%20centre.%20Now%20there%20are%20many%20more%20such%20centres%20for%20women%20across%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20coach%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndian%20women%20wrestlers%20are%20doing%20very%20well%2C%20and%20we%20are%20expecting%20a%20couple%20of%20medals%20from%20them%20in%20Paris%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFamily%20support%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20when%20society%20was%20not%20accepting%20the%20women%20from%20the%20khap%20land%20of%20Haryana%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20wrestling%20world%2C%20it%20was%20the%20unconditional%20support%20of%20family%2C%20especially%20the%20parents%2C%20that%20kept%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20our%20relatives%20are%20from%20a%20sports%20background%2C%20so%20they%20had%20no%20issues%20with%20putting%20the%20family%20girls%20in%20wrestling%2C%20but%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20so%20forthcoming%20from%20the%20ones%20who%20weren%E2%80%99t.%20Whenever%20they%20used%20to%20meet%20us%2C%20their%20main%20concern%20was%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F293092%2Fnikhat-zareen-wins-commonwealth-games-medal-for-india-boxing-world-champion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20would%20be%20her%20future%20if%20Reetika%20didn%E2%80%99t%20excel%20in%20wrestling%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20But%20her%20father%20stood%20by%20her%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20her%20mother%2C%20Neelam%20Devi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEver%20since%20Reetika%20earned%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20quota%20place%2C%20the%20same%20relatives%20have%20been%20wishing%20her%20success.%20Hope%20no%20other%20girl%20has%20to%20face%20any%20more%20sarcasm%2C%20especially%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350331%2Fparvej-khan-haryana-farmer-son-indian-track-athlete-runner-won-gold-sec-championship-usa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethose%20from%20rural%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Neelam%20Devi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20684px)%20100vw%2C%20684px%5C%22%